# API Endpoints

FastAPI REST API layer with JWT and API token authentication, organized into two router groups.

## App Entry Point (`overmind/main.py`)

- Single `FastAPI` instance (no factory pattern)
- On startup: initializes `ClientCacheManager`, auth providers, Celery app, runs `ensure_default_user()` for first-run bootstrap
- Serves built frontend SPA from `frontend_dist/` when present (API + SPA on single port)
- Health check: `GET /health` тЖТ `{"status": "healthy"}`
- CORS: allows all origins (development mode)

## Router Structure (`overmind/api/v1/router.py`)

Two router groups, both mounted at `/api/v1`:

### `core_api_router` тАФ all endpoints require auth

```python
core_api_router = APIRouter(dependencies=[Depends(get_current_user)])
```

- `/traces` тАФ trace listing/detail
- `/spans` тАФ span feedback, evaluation
- `/prompts` тАФ prompt CRUD, criteria management
- `/backtesting` тАФ backtest model listing, run triggers

### `core_auth_router` тАФ mixed auth (per-endpoint)

- `/suggestions` тАФ suggestion listing, feedback
- `/agents` тАФ agent listing, detail, metadata
- `/agent-reviews` тАФ review spans, update descriptions
- `/jobs` тАФ job CRUD, trigger, status
- `/onboarding` тАФ onboarding state
- `/traces` (OTLP) тАФ trace ingestion (separate auth: API token or proxy token)
- `/iam` тАФ users (login is public), projects, tokens

## Authentication (`overmind/api/v1/helpers/authentication.py`)

### Two auth methods:

1. **API Token**: `X-API-Token` header with prefix `ovr_core_`. Token is SHA-256 hashed and looked up in DB. Cached in Valkey.
1. **JWT**: `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header. HS256 algorithm, 30-min expiry. Validated and cached in Valkey.

### `AuthenticatedUserOrToken`

The auth dependency returns this object containing:

- `user: UserModel` тАФ the authenticated user
- `token: TokenModel | None` тАФ set when auth was via API token (contains `project_id`, `organisation_id`)
- Enterprise fields: `clerk_org_id`, `permissions`

### `get_current_user` dependency

Tries API token first, then JWT bearer token. Returns `AuthenticatedUserOrToken` or raises 401.

### `RBACAuthenticationProvider`

Pluggable auth provider. Core mode uses basic auth (no RBAC permission checking). Enterprise overrides with full RBAC.

## Key Endpoint Groups

### Agents (`overmind/api/v1/endpoints/agents.py`)

- `GET /agents` тАФ list agents with analytics (hourly buckets, job status, suggestions)
- `GET /agents/{slug}/detail` тАФ agent detail with prompt versions
- `PUT /agents/{slug}/metadata` тАФ update agent name, tags

### Jobs (`overmind/api/v1/endpoints/jobs.py`)

- `POST /jobs` тАФ create job (validates eligibility first)
- `GET /jobs` тАФ list with running status sync
- `POST /jobs/extract-templates` тАФ trigger agent discovery
- `POST /jobs/{slug}/score` тАФ trigger judge scoring (auto-generates missing criteria and description before validation)
- `POST /jobs/{slug}/tune` тАФ trigger prompt tuning
- `POST /jobs/{job_id}/trigger` тАФ manually trigger pending job

### Traces (`overmind/api/v1/endpoints/traces.py`)

- `GET /traces/trace/{trace_id}` тАФ trace detail with spans
- `GET /traces/list` тАФ paginated trace list with filters

### Spans (`overmind/api/v1/endpoints/spans.py`)

- `PATCH /spans/{span_id}/feedback` тАФ update span feedback score
- `POST /spans/evaluate` тАФ trigger evaluation for specific spans

### Prompts (`overmind/api/v1/endpoints/prompts.py`)

- `POST /prompts` тАФ create prompt
- `GET /prompts` тАФ list prompts
- `PUT /prompts/criteria` тАФ update evaluation criteria
- `POST /prompts/criteria/generate` тАФ generate criteria via LLM

### Suggestions (`overmind/api/v1/endpoints/suggestions.py`)

- `GET /suggestions` тАФ list suggestions
- `POST /suggestions/{id}/feedback` тАФ vote/feedback on suggestion

